------

Significant changes made to inuitcss:
 - All references to Inuitcss are removed
 - All variables, mixins and class names prefix with inuit are prefixed with
 - Inuitcss repositories collected into one single repository
 - Consistent placement of responsive suffixes and prefixes
 - Keep both responsive and non-responsive classes in the same files
 - Made it possible to toggle modules not only through includes but also through variables
 - Always use box-sizing: border-box;
 - Responsive settings and tools included by default
 - Added collections to make it easier for developers to get up-and-running with the essentials
 - Added an index of all variables
 - Collected all variables into settings files instead of putting them into each module's file
 - Prefixed utility helper classes with u-
 - Prefixed object classes with o-
